---
title: Quick Sesame-Teriyaki Shrimp Stir-Fry with Bok Choy and Jasmine Rice
description: This low-prep dinner packs in big flavour hits with teriyaki sauce, ginger and sesame. Throw some rice on, get the shrimp in a pan and dinner will on the table before you know it!
